  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Driver
    Driver class runs all the necessary classese to read in an input file, omit words, and track word position and count using binary search trees and a hash table for ommitted words.
    Hash
    Hash class creates the hash table for the omitted words to be compared to the input text
    LinePosition
    LinePosition class tracks the line position and line number for a word in the input file
    ObjectBinaryTree
    class ObjectTreeNode provides methods to build and manipulate a binary search tree comprised of nodes
    ObjectList
    class ObjectList creates and manipulates linked lists composed of nodes.
    ObjectListNode
    class ObjectListNode provides methods to build and manipulate nodes in a linear linked list
    ObjectTreeNode
    class ObjectTreeNode provides methods to build and manipulate nodes in a binary search tree
    Word
    Word class creates word Objects to be placed into the binary search tree
    Xref
    Xref class reads the input file and creates binary search tree to make the word index and track the word count and position
